<figureCitation captionStart="Figure 9" captionStartId="F7691952" captionText="Figure 9. Angarotipula laetipennis A mating; B young larvae foraging; C last instar larva; D last instar larva, stress state; E newly-pupated pupa; F Pupa shell, female and male." figureDoi="10.3897/BDJ.10.e82427.figure9" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/644865" pageId="0" pageNumber="82427">9</figureCitation>
E).
</paragraph>
